title: Luxury Home Slideshow: 35 Washington Ave., Savannah
text:
Photos Jennifer Menster/Savannah Morning News - This home at 35 Washington Ave., Savannah, is listed for $995,000. By Savannah Morning News We continue our look at luxury homes for sale in Savannah with a visit to 35 Washington Avenue.
Click here to take a photographic tour of this Ardsley Park home. This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath house is currently for sale by Keller Williams Realtor Ron Melander and listed for $995,000.
